      "file_path": "feature-controller-logging/src/main/feature/config/logback-controller.xml",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 50,
      "message": "So is the ask to have multiple included logback configurations per controller rather than one logback-controller file? Example: logback-casablance.xml and logback-amsterdam.xml rather than a logback-controller.xml that contains the configurations for those loggers? The controller specific logback files would be apart of the feature-amsterdam and feature-casablanca modules in drools-applications if I am understanding correctly.",
